name: Qr_Boas_Vindas_Doadin_Trata_Celular
queryText:
SELECT
  A.CPF_CNPJ,
  A.ID_PROPOSTA,
  '55' + REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(A.CELULAR, '(', ''), ')', ''), ' ', ''), '-', '') AS CELULAR
FROM Tb_Boas_Vindas_Doadin_Prospostas A
WHERE CELULAR IS NOT NULL
targetDescription: Publico Inicial - Propostas elegiveis para campanha de boas vindas Doadin
